==Introduction==
「九九艦爆」の後継として開発された高速性能を誇る艦上爆撃機「彗星」。<br>
液冷発動機を装備。当時の一般的な戦闘機より速く、護衛の零戦すら振り切れる高速性とも言われます。<br>
整備の難しい機体ですが、高速艦爆としての完成度は高く、ぜひ機動部隊の中核として運用してくださいね。

''Boasting high-speed performance, the successor of the "[[Type 99 Dive Bomber|Type 99 Carrier-based Bomber]]", the "Suisei".<br>
''It is equipped with a liquid-cooled engine. It is faster than typical fighters, even its [[Type 21 Zero Fighter|Zero-fighter]] escorts.''<br>
''Although it is difficult to maintain, its excellence as a carrier-based dive bomber is undeniable. Please do use it as the core of your mobile squadron.''
==Notes==
Buildable. Stock equipment of [[Taihou]], and all remodelled CVs and CVLs except for [[Houshou|Houshou Kai]], [[Chitose|Chitose Carrier]] and [[Chiyoda|Chiyoda Carrier]].

== Trivia ==
* Although it can be equipped on CVLs in Kancolle, the Suisei's high landing speed made it unsuitable for operation from smaller carriers due to the long flight deck required.
